1
00:00:15,150 --> 00:00:18,150
Shall we take the kids out for dessert? I think they will like it.

2
00:00:18,950 --> 00:00:20,150
Don't come here again.

3
00:00:20,650 --> 00:00:21,150
Why?

4
00:00:21,650 --> 00:00:24,150
My world and your world are different.

5
00:00:24,650 --> 00:00:25,150
Good luck.

6
00:00:26,150 --> 00:00:29,150
If someone sees Dong's body in this condition, we'll be in trouble.

7
00:00:30,150 --> 00:00:34,150
I think we should hurry and cremate Dong's body.

8
00:00:34,750 --> 00:00:36,150
But I think I think we shouldn't burn it yet.

9
00:00:36,550 --> 00:00:39,150
Maybe someone will take this opportunity to frame you again.

10
00:00:39,650 --> 00:00:41,150
Wait another seven days.

11
00:00:41,850 --> 00:00:44,150
If relatives or someone else doesn't complain about Dong's death,

12
00:00:44,750 --> 00:00:45,150
until that day, we can burn the body.

13
00:00:46,150 --> 00:00:51,150
Do you think Li has something to do with the death of a worker?

14
00:00:51,750 --> 00:00:54,150
I have brought you the news. How you'll handle it

15
00:00:54,650 --> 00:00:56,150
is up to you.

16
00:00:56,650 --> 00:00:59,150
We will use this to destroy his credibility

17
00:01:00,150 --> 00:01:03,150
and remove Big Brother from the head position of the Five Dragons Association.

18
00:01:04,150 --> 00:01:07,150
Doing this is like bringing enemies to our home.

19
00:01:07,750 --> 00:01:08,150
I'm really curious

20
00:01:09,150 --> 00:01:13,150
what method Mr. Ma will use to deal with Madam Li and Dong's body.

21
00:03:03,150 --> 00:03:04,150
Madam.

22
00:03:06,150 --> 00:03:08,150
I let the servant prepare the car for you. Let's go.

23
00:03:10,150 --> 00:03:13,150
The body is finally getting burned.

24
00:03:14,150 --> 00:03:18,150
I'm scared that his relatives will show up every day.

25
00:03:18,750 --> 00:03:21,150
Or someone will suspect Dong's death again.

26
00:03:23,150 --> 00:03:24,150
And everything is fine now, right?

27
00:03:25,150 --> 00:03:26,150
Yes, Madam.

28
00:03:28,150 --> 00:03:30,150
Are you going to Dong's funeral?

29
00:03:33,150 --> 00:03:35,150
Why are you and Nuan dressing like this?

30
00:03:35,850 --> 00:03:37,150
Oh, it's Dong's funeral.

31
00:03:37,750 --> 00:03:40,150
Madam and I want to participate the funeral as well.

32
00:03:40,850 --> 00:03:42,150
We had lived together here for a long time. It's his last day.

33
00:03:43,150 --> 00:03:45,150
I'd like to send him as well.

34
00:03:49,150 --> 00:03:51,150
Are you ready?

35
00:03:54,150 --> 00:03:55,150
Sir.

36
00:03:56,150 --> 00:04:00,150
Are you coming with me? Didn't you say you let me handle this?

37
00:04:01,150 --> 00:04:03,150
At first, I thought I wouldn't go.

38
00:04:03,850 --> 00:04:07,150
But Chan said that I should go to make merit for Dong.

39
00:04:09,150 --> 00:04:14,150
Well, last night, I dreamed that the spirit of Dong came here howling.

40
00:04:15,150 --> 00:04:18,150
His face was furious as if he wanted to say something.

41
00:04:18,650 --> 00:04:20,150
What did he want to say?

42
00:04:20,850 --> 00:04:24,150
He would have wanted to say someone intentionally killed him

43
00:04:25,150 --> 00:04:28,150
and wanted me to help catch the culprit.

44
00:04:29,150 --> 00:04:32,150
Dong stole things and ran away and drowned.

45
00:04:32,850 --> 00:04:34,150
Nobody killed him.

46
00:04:35,150 --> 00:04:36,150
Stop blaming me.

47
00:04:38,150 --> 00:04:39,150
Madam.

48
00:04:40,150 --> 00:04:43,150
I haven't accused you of killing Dong.

49
00:04:44,150 --> 00:04:46,150
Don't be scared beforehand.

50
00:04:47,150 --> 00:04:50,150
What I said was just a dream.

51
00:04:51,150 --> 00:04:53,150
Hey, enough. Stop arguing.

52
00:04:54,150 --> 00:04:56,150
Let's hurry to the temple and make merit for Dong.

53
00:04:57,150 --> 00:04:58,150
Everyone would be wait for us by now.

54
00:05:00,150 --> 00:05:01,150
Everyone?

55
00:05:02,150 --> 00:05:04,150
Yes, everyone.

56
00:05:05,150 --> 00:05:07,150
Shall we go?

57
00:05:14,150 --> 00:05:15,150
Sir, let's go.

58
00:05:21,150 --> 00:05:31,150
(Prayer)

59
00:06:00,150 --> 00:06:02,150
The prayer has finished.

60
00:06:02,650 --> 00:06:04,150
I'll let the staff take Dong's body for cremation now.

61
00:06:07,150 --> 00:06:10,150
But according to Thai tradition, the dead's face must be washed first.

62
00:06:14,150 --> 00:06:16,150
Mr. Song is Chinese, so you may not know.

63
00:06:16,650 --> 00:06:18,150
Nuan, tell the staff to open the coffin.

64
00:06:19,150 --> 00:06:20,150
Yes, Madam.

65
00:06:21,150 --> 00:06:22,150
Don't open it.

66
00:06:32,150 --> 00:06:33,150
Why?

67
00:06:37,150 --> 00:06:38,150
Dong's body had been dead for several days.

68
00:06:39,150 --> 00:06:40,150
It would have swollen and bloated.

69
00:06:41,150 --> 00:06:42,150
It must be ugly to look at.

70
00:06:43,150 --> 00:06:44,150
It's fine to me.

71
00:06:45,150 --> 00:06:48,150
So we can learn that

72
00:06:48,550 --> 00:06:50,150
Nothing stays forever.

73
00:06:56,150 --> 00:06:59,150
You don't have to do it actually. Though it's a custom,

74
00:06:59,750 --> 00:07:02,150
but if it's inconvenient or inappropriate, then don't do it.

75
00:07:06,150 --> 00:07:08,150
So do as the monk said.

76
00:07:09,150 --> 00:07:12,150
Let the staff carry his body to do the cremation.

77
00:07:43,150 --> 00:07:44,150
Stop.

78
00:08:07,150 --> 00:08:09,150
Don't move the body anywhere.

79
00:08:11,150 --> 00:08:13,150
What is this, Mr. Ma, Aunt Xiao Tong?

80
00:08:14,150 --> 00:08:15,150
Why are you interfering this?

81
00:08:16,150 --> 00:08:19,150
Yes, why do you bring the police here?

82
00:08:21,150 --> 00:08:23,150
Ma told me

83
00:08:24,150 --> 00:08:26,150
that a worker from Song Family's had died.

84
00:08:27,150 --> 00:08:29,150
But there's something weird relevant to Li.

85
00:08:30,150 --> 00:08:33,150
So he wanted us to witnesses and find out the truth.

86
00:08:34,150 --> 00:08:37,150
But I still don't believe that much, Big Brother.

87
00:08:38,150 --> 00:08:40,150
I just want to see it with my own eyes

88
00:08:41,150 --> 00:08:42,150
what exactly happened.

89
00:08:55,150 --> 00:08:56,150
I'm sorry, Big Brother,

90
00:08:57,150 --> 00:08:59,150
that I didn't tell you before.

91
00:08:59,200 --> 00:09:03,150
The person who died was a relative of my worker.

92
00:09:04,150 --> 00:09:07,150
He suspected the death of his nephew.

93
00:09:07,650 --> 00:09:10,150
So I have to take him here.

94
00:09:17,150 --> 00:09:20,150
My name is Zhan, an elder brother of Dong's mom.

95
00:09:21,150 --> 00:09:23,150
Dong was close to the relatives on his father's side.

96
00:09:24,150 --> 00:09:27,150
When his parents died, everyone parted.

97
00:09:28,150 --> 00:09:30,150
I just found out that he was dead.

98
00:09:38,150 --> 00:09:41,150
We've been looking for Dong's relatives for several days.

99
00:09:41,750 --> 00:09:43,150
Why are you showing up now?

100
00:09:44,150 --> 00:09:47,150
Did you secretly accept money from someone to lander us?

101
00:09:52,150 --> 00:09:53,150
As I said,

102
00:09:54,150 --> 00:09:57,150
my worker heard that

103
00:09:58,150 --> 00:09:59,150
before his death,

104
00:10:00,150 --> 00:10:02,150
Dong had a fight with Li.

105
00:10:10,150 --> 00:10:12,150
So I need to take the police to do an autopsy first

106
00:10:13,150 --> 00:10:17,150
to see what the real cause of death is.

107
00:10:19,150 --> 00:10:21,150
Was it an accident or a murder?

108
00:10:38,150 --> 00:10:39,150
Police officers.

109
00:10:50,150 --> 00:10:53,150
Mr. Zhan, come and see if this is your relative's body.

110
00:10:54,150 --> 00:10:57,150
If it is correct, he will be sent for an autopsy to determine the cause of death.

111
00:11:07,150 --> 00:11:08,150
Open it.

112
00:11:23,150 --> 00:11:25,150
I thought it might be like this.

113
00:11:26,150 --> 00:11:27,150
So I prepare a backup plan.

114
00:11:44,150 --> 00:11:45,150
The coffin must be made of thin wood.

115
00:11:46,150 --> 00:11:48,150
So the rats can eat the corpse.

116
00:12:08,150 --> 00:12:13,150
The face is ruined like this. Can you still confirm that this is your relative?

117
00:12:30,150 --> 00:12:31,150
This is not Dong's body.

118
00:12:38,150 --> 00:12:39,150
What do you mean?

119
00:12:40,150 --> 00:12:41,150
You can get caught by the police if you talk nonsense.

120
00:12:41,750 --> 00:12:42,150
Look at it.

121
00:12:43,150 --> 00:12:44,150
There are may grey hairs.

122
00:12:45,150 --> 00:12:48,150
Dong was still young. Why did he got so many grey hairs?

123
00:12:49,150 --> 00:12:50,150
Another thing,

124
00:12:50,850 --> 00:12:53,150
He had been taken out of the water several days ago.

125
00:12:53,750 --> 00:12:56,150
The body must be soft and deteriorating, but what is this?

126
00:12:56,650 --> 00:12:58,150
The skin looks like a normal dead.

127
00:13:10,150 --> 00:13:13,150
If it's not Dong's body, whose body is this?

128
00:13:23,150 --> 00:13:26,150
Anyway, I need to bring the body back to check to see what happened.

129
00:13:26,850 --> 00:13:29,150
If there's a progress, I will immediately inform you all.

130
00:14:15,150 --> 00:14:17,150
How could something like this happen?

131
00:14:18,150 --> 00:14:19,150
Didn't you say you couldn't find his relatives?

132
00:14:20,150 --> 00:14:22,150
Then why did his relative show up today?

133
00:14:23,150 --> 00:14:25,150
Or do you have anything to do with this, Li?

134
00:14:26,150 --> 00:14:27,150
Where is Dong's body?

135
00:14:28,150 --> 00:14:29,150
I don't know.

136
00:14:30,150 --> 00:14:31,150
You really don't know?

137
00:14:32,150 --> 00:14:34,150
Previously, you still let Jia watch over the body there.

138
00:14:35,150 --> 00:14:37,150
Watching over the corpse or doing what?

139
00:14:37,850 --> 00:14:38,150
Shut your mouth.

140
00:14:39,150 --> 00:14:40,150
Don't think I don't know

141
00:14:41,150 --> 00:14:45,150
that Mr. Ma brought the police today because you told him the news.

142
00:14:46,150 --> 00:14:48,150
Hoping he will get me and my son, right?

143
00:14:50,150 --> 00:14:51,150
Is it true, Chan?

144
00:14:52,150 --> 00:14:53,150
Why would I do that?

145
00:14:54,150 --> 00:14:56,150
Everyone knows what kind of man Mr. Ma is.

146
00:14:57,150 --> 00:15:00,150
He is trying to destroy the Song family's reputation.

147
00:15:01,150 --> 00:15:04,150
The workers gossiped about Dong's death themselves.

148
00:15:06,150 --> 00:15:10,150
Mr. Ma heard it and made a big deal.

149
00:15:16,150 --> 00:15:17,150
That's true.

150
00:15:19,150 --> 00:15:21,150
Ma hopes to destroy the reputation of me and the Song family many times.

151
00:15:23,150 --> 00:15:25,150
And if he succeeds this time,

152
00:15:26,150 --> 00:15:30,150
he will probably use this reason to remove me from the leader position of the association.

153
00:15:35,150 --> 00:15:37,150
You two listen carefully.

154
00:15:39,150 --> 00:15:44,150
If the officials know who got involved in Dong's death,

155
00:15:45,150 --> 00:15:47,150
I won't help any of you at all.

156
00:15:50,150 --> 00:15:52,150
And if it affects the Five Dragons Association,

157
00:15:54,150 --> 00:15:58,150
I will punish that person until the very end.

158
00:16:24,150 --> 00:16:26,150
Is it you?

159
00:16:30,150 --> 00:16:32,150
Did you tell Mr. Ma to mess with this?

160
00:16:33,150 --> 00:16:34,150
Why did you do that?

161
00:16:35,150 --> 00:16:38,150
Do you want to borrow someone else's hand to get rid of Madam and Tian for me?

162
00:16:39,150 --> 00:16:41,150
Please, don't do it again.

163
00:16:41,850 --> 00:16:45,150
I told you that I never wanted anything that wasn't mine.

164
00:16:46,150 --> 00:16:47,150
Please stop.

165
00:16:48,150 --> 00:16:51,150
Do you know how many people will suffer from what you did?

166
00:16:52,150 --> 00:16:55,150
The person who is in trouble is a murderer.

167
00:16:55,650 --> 00:16:57,150
Why are you protecting them?

168
00:16:59,150 --> 00:17:02,150
You tell me to stop doing this for you? I can't.

169
00:17:05,150 --> 00:17:10,150
I will do everything to make you the leader of the clan instead of Tian.

170
00:17:43,150 --> 00:17:48,150
Mr. Yang, drink something sweet here.

171
00:17:49,150 --> 00:17:52,150
Even if I drink a jar, it won't help me.

172
00:17:53,150 --> 00:17:56,150
Dong's death is now a big mess.

173
00:17:57,150 --> 00:18:01,150
Both the officials and people from the association are involved in this matter.

174
00:18:02,150 --> 00:18:04,150
I can't predict how this will end.

175
00:18:05,150 --> 00:18:07,150
We won't be able to do anything.

176
00:18:08,150 --> 00:18:09,150
We just have to wait.

177
00:18:09,850 --> 00:18:11,150
The authorities have now come in to handled it.

178
00:18:11,850 --> 00:18:16,150
Once we find Dong's body, we'll soon know the cause of death.

179
00:18:18,150 --> 00:18:21,150
Since the body is gone, everyone now focuses on Madam Li.

180
00:18:22,150 --> 00:18:25,150
Because earlier, she told Aunt Jia to sleep at the temple to watch over Dong's body.

181
00:18:26,150 --> 00:18:28,150
But we still don't know the truth.

182
00:18:28,850 --> 00:18:31,150
I think we shouldn't judge anything yet.

183
00:18:36,150 --> 00:18:38,150
How is Tian now?

184
00:19:03,150 --> 00:19:04,150
Before his death,

185
00:19:05,150 --> 00:19:06,150
Dong had a fight with Li.

186
00:19:15,150 --> 00:19:16,150
This is not Dong's body.

187
00:19:17,150 --> 00:19:20,150
If it's not Dong's body, whose body is this?

188
00:19:30,150 --> 00:19:31,150
Tian.

189
00:19:33,150 --> 00:19:34,150
Yang.

190
00:19:43,150 --> 00:19:46,150
I thought you were going to see Bua.

191
00:19:47,150 --> 00:19:48,150
So I waited for you there.

192
00:19:53,150 --> 00:19:54,150
Bua and I are worried about you.

193
00:19:57,150 --> 00:19:58,150
Thank you.

194
00:20:06,150 --> 00:20:10,150
If I tell you not to feel stressed, not to think too much,

195
00:20:11,150 --> 00:20:13,150
you probably can't do it, right?

196
00:20:15,150 --> 00:20:19,150
And if I tell you to tell me everything,

197
00:20:20,150 --> 00:20:22,150
I don't know if you want to do it or not.

198
00:20:28,150 --> 00:20:30,150
So what should I do, Tian?

199
00:20:32,150 --> 00:20:33,150
How can I help you?

200
00:20:38,150 --> 00:20:39,150
Yang.

201
00:20:43,150 --> 00:20:44,150
I don't know what to do.

202
00:20:47,150 --> 00:20:49,150
I'm scared, I'm so scared.

203
00:20:51,150 --> 00:20:53,150
The story is like this because of me.

204
00:20:54,150 --> 00:20:57,150
Dong died because of my secret.

205
00:20:58,150 --> 00:21:00,150
Calm down, Tian. Calm down first.

206
00:21:00,850 --> 00:21:02,150
I should have been known since that day.

207
00:21:03,150 --> 00:21:07,150
When Dong behaved badly towards me and Mother defended him.

208
00:21:07,550 --> 00:21:08,150
It might not be what you think.

209
00:21:08,550 --> 00:21:09,150
It is.

210
00:21:11,150 --> 00:21:12,150
I know it.

211
00:21:17,150 --> 00:21:18,150
Actually…

212
00:21:21,150 --> 00:21:22,150
Actually…

213
00:21:25,150 --> 00:21:26,150
I'm...

214
00:21:32,150 --> 00:21:33,150
I'm...

215
00:21:40,150 --> 00:21:41,150
Don't say anything.

216
00:21:44,150 --> 00:21:45,150
Don't say anything.

217
00:21:48,150 --> 00:21:50,150
Don't think about anything.

218
00:21:51,150 --> 00:21:52,150
No matter what happens,

219
00:21:55,150 --> 00:21:57,150
No matter what you are,

220
00:22:00,150 --> 00:22:02,150
I will be by your side.

221
00:22:08,150 --> 00:22:10,150
I'll find a way to help you.

222
00:22:22,150 --> 00:22:23,150
it's alright.

223
00:22:25,150 --> 00:22:26,150
Thanks a lot, Yang.

224
00:22:48,150 --> 00:22:49,150
Mother.

225
00:22:51,150 --> 00:22:52,150
Come in.

226
00:22:59,150 --> 00:23:00,150
What's the matter?

227
00:23:11,150 --> 00:23:12,150
I'm not happy at all.

228
00:23:13,150 --> 00:23:15,150
Dong's body disappeared like this.

229
00:23:15,650 --> 00:23:18,150
Everyone thought that you have something to do with it.

230
00:23:20,150 --> 00:23:21,150
Mother.

231
00:23:22,150 --> 00:23:25,150
Dong died because he knew my secret, right?

232
00:23:27,150 --> 00:23:29,150
And the body vanished like this,

233
00:23:31,150 --> 00:23:32,150
it's connected, right?

234
00:23:34,150 --> 00:23:35,150
Don't worry.

235
00:23:37,150 --> 00:23:38,150
This is not about you.

236
00:23:39,150 --> 00:23:42,150
But we should consider what Aunt Chan said.

237
00:23:43,150 --> 00:23:44,150
Everything seems to fit.

238
00:23:46,150 --> 00:23:48,150
People are thinking of me badly right now.

239
00:23:49,150 --> 00:23:51,150
Whether it's Chan or Mr. Ma.

240
00:23:52,150 --> 00:23:55,150
They all want to take advantage of Dong's death.

241
00:23:55,750 --> 00:23:58,150
Using this to attack us to become the leader of the association.

242
00:24:01,150 --> 00:24:04,150
And now your father is not satisfied with me and blame me too.

243
00:24:06,150 --> 00:24:08,150
If you don't trust me too, I'll probably have no one left.

244
00:24:09,150 --> 00:24:10,150
Mother.

245
00:24:11,150 --> 00:24:13,150
I didn't suspect or didn't trust you.

246
00:24:15,150 --> 00:24:20,150
But I don't want anyone to die because of my secret.

247
00:24:22,150 --> 00:24:23,150
Now the police come in.

248
00:24:25,150 --> 00:24:28,150
Let them take care of everything.

249
00:24:30,150 --> 00:24:32,150
We will know the truth soon.

250
00:24:46,150 --> 00:24:48,150
If the worker's body being switched is true,

251
00:24:49,150 --> 00:24:52,150
It's suspicious why the worker's body should be hidden.

252
00:24:54,150 --> 00:24:55,150
What exactly is it?

253
00:24:55,650 --> 00:24:58,150
Mr. Ma hurriedly called mt to see Dong's body at the temple.

254
00:24:59,150 --> 00:25:02,150
He seemed to know from the beginning that there was something strange about it.

255
00:25:03,150 --> 00:25:06,150
Ma waited for the moment to attack Big Brother

256
00:25:07,150 --> 00:25:10,150
to claim the head position of the association for a long time.

257
00:25:11,150 --> 00:25:13,150
He hopes we can support him.

258
00:25:16,150 --> 00:25:20,150
I've heard that the Mr. Song had been blaming Madam Li and Madam Chan.

259
00:25:21,150 --> 00:25:24,150
That means he doesn't trust his two wives as well.

260
00:25:25,150 --> 00:25:28,150
So which side should we choose?

261
00:25:29,150 --> 00:25:31,150
Mr. Song or Mr. Ma.

262
00:25:32,150 --> 00:25:36,150
In this situation, we should not choose a side.

263
00:25:37,150 --> 00:25:40,150
We should be neutral.

264
00:25:49,150 --> 00:25:57,150
Hey, don't worry. Order as you want.
265

265
00:25:57,150 --> 00:25:58,150
Who wants money? Money!

266
00:25:59,150 --> 00:26:00,150
That's...

267
00:26:01,150 --> 00:26:02,150
Dong's uncle.

268
00:26:07,150 --> 00:26:08,150
No need to hurry.

269
00:26:10,150 --> 00:26:11,150
Why is he wealthy now?

270
00:26:21,150 --> 00:26:24,150
If everyone knows that you were the one who told Mr. Ma,

271
00:26:24,650 --> 00:26:26,150
we'll be in trouble.

272
00:26:26,850 --> 00:26:29,150
But if Ma helps expose Madam Li and Jia,

273
00:26:30,150 --> 00:26:31,150
they'll be in trouble, not us.

274
00:26:32,150 --> 00:26:34,150
Now the police interfere,

275
00:26:34,850 --> 00:26:37,150
they must prove if that the body is Dong's.

276
00:26:38,150 --> 00:26:42,150
If it isn't, they must find the body until it is found.

277
00:26:43,150 --> 00:26:45,150
If we get the body and let the cop prove it,

278
00:26:46,150 --> 00:26:50,150
we'll know what they're trying to hide, right?

279
00:26:51,150 --> 00:26:52,150
Correct.

280
00:26:51,500 --> 00:25:54,000
I'm rich today. It's my treat.

281
00:26:58,150 --> 00:27:02,150
Madam Li and Old Jia won't get away this time.

282
00:27:09,150 --> 00:27:11,150
Auntie, come take a look here.

283
00:27:11,750 --> 00:27:12,150
What's wrong?

284
00:27:12,350 --> 00:27:13,150
Well, hurry.

285
00:27:14,150 --> 00:27:15,150
Why are you shouting?

286
00:27:15,450 --> 00:27:16,150
Follow me.

287
00:27:16,850 --> 00:27:19,150
What's wrong with you? I'm going to fall down.

288
00:27:22,150 --> 00:27:25,150
What kind of mushrooms are these? Why are they blooming so much?

289
00:27:25,650 --> 00:27:29,150
Right? I've been picking vegetables and bamboo shoots here for ten years.

290
00:27:29,750 --> 00:27:31,150
I've never seen anything like this.

291
00:27:42,150 --> 00:27:44,150
So let's get them all. Quickly.

292
00:27:46,150 --> 00:27:47,150
So many of them.

293
00:28:01,150 --> 00:28:02,150
I made herbal soup for you.

294
00:28:03,150 --> 00:28:04,150
Please drink it.

295
00:28:06,150 --> 00:28:08,150
What should I do next?

296
00:28:10,150 --> 00:28:11,150
Don't be afraid, Madam.

297
00:28:12,150 --> 00:28:15,150
If something happens, I will be responsible for it alone.

298
00:28:20,150 --> 00:28:21,150
Jia.

299
00:28:24,150 --> 00:28:27,150
So how did you handle Dong's body?

300
00:28:29,150 --> 00:28:33,150
I was in a hurry, so I hid it around here.

301
00:28:34,150 --> 00:28:37,150
But don't worry, I'll go back and deal with it again soon.

302
00:28:49,150 --> 00:28:52,150
Did the mushrooms from Dong's body grow this much?

303
00:28:56,150 --> 00:28:58,150
Let's collect more.

304
00:29:01,150 --> 00:29:02,150
Oh, Auntie Jia.

305
00:29:04,150 --> 00:29:05,150
Are you coming to pick mushrooms as well?

306
00:29:07,150 --> 00:29:10,150
It's delicious, right? We have already collected one round.

307
00:29:10,550 --> 00:29:12,150
We liked the mushrooms so much that we come back to collect them again.

308
00:29:13,150 --> 00:29:14,150
Are you guys picking mushrooms to eat?

309
00:29:15,150 --> 00:29:18,150
Yes, this mushroom is plump and delicious.

310
00:29:18,650 --> 00:29:20,150
The people in the kitchen were really impressed.

311
00:29:21,150 --> 00:29:23,150
You don't need to do. I'll do it for you.

312
00:29:24,150 --> 00:29:25,150
Move, let me do it.

313
00:29:28,150 --> 00:29:29,150
Come quickly.

314
00:29:31,150 --> 00:29:32,150
Chen.

315
00:29:33,150 --> 00:29:34,150
Yes, Aunt Jia.

316
00:29:36,150 --> 00:29:38,150
What are you guys doing here?

317
00:29:39,150 --> 00:29:41,150
Mr. Song ordered me to build more bunkers.

318
00:29:41,550 --> 00:29:42,150
Why does he want it here?

319
00:29:42,550 --> 00:29:44,150
He wants the bunkers to be hidden around.

320
00:29:46,150 --> 00:29:47,150
I'll off to work.

321
00:29:51,150 --> 00:29:52,150
Let's go to work.

322
00:29:54,150 --> 00:29:56,150
Build a bunker?

323
00:29:56,850 --> 00:29:58,150
Then it will take a long time to finish.

324
00:29:58,650 --> 00:30:02,150
Yes, a lot of workers must be hanging around in the area.

325
00:30:02,750 --> 00:30:04,150
It wouldn't be that easy to dig up Dong's body.

326
00:30:05,150 --> 00:30:08,150
The people in the kitchen collecting mushrooms and the workers are there.

327
00:30:09,150 --> 00:30:12,150
You should go talk to Mr. Song build the bunkers somewhere else.

328
00:30:13,150 --> 00:30:14,150
No.

329
00:30:15,150 --> 00:30:16,150
Instead of the digging up the body quietly,

330
00:30:17,150 --> 00:30:20,150
Chan will turn to focus on what we did to that area.

331
00:30:21,150 --> 00:30:22,150
It will get worse.

332
00:30:23,150 --> 00:30:25,150
But we have to find a way to get rid of the body.

333
00:30:34,150 --> 00:30:36,150
Thank you for bringing the snacks for me.

334
00:30:37,150 --> 00:30:38,150
Take some fruit as a gift for your father when you go back.

335
00:30:44,150 --> 00:30:45,150
Pin.

336
00:30:47,150 --> 00:30:48,150
Yes？

337
00:30:49,150 --> 00:30:51,150
Is anything bothering you?

338
00:30:52,150 --> 00:30:53,150
You can tell me.

339
00:30:59,150 --> 00:31:01,150
Where are you going, Yang?

340
00:31:02,150 --> 00:31:03,150
Let's talk.

341
00:31:05,150 --> 00:31:06,150
It's okay.

342
00:31:06,650 --> 00:31:09,150
I don't want be a third wheeler.

343
00:31:10,150 --> 00:31:11,150
I'm leaving.

344
00:31:11,650 --> 00:31:13,150
The two of us are talking and having fun.

345
00:31:14,150 --> 00:31:16,150
No one interrupts us.

346
00:31:17,150 --> 00:31:19,150
I wish you a happy afternoon.

347
00:31:20,150 --> 00:31:23,150
Being with my fiancé makes me happy already.

348
00:31:24,150 --> 00:31:28,150
I forget that you don't care about love

349
00:31:28,650 --> 00:31:29,150
because it's nonsense.

350
00:31:30,150 --> 00:31:34,150
Love is not nonsense. It's the people.

351
00:31:37,150 --> 00:31:38,150
Yes, it's me who is nonsense.

352
00:31:51,150 --> 00:31:52,150
Pin.

353
00:31:54,150 --> 00:31:57,150
Have you heard about the folk tale titled Butterfly Lovers?

354
00:32:00,150 --> 00:32:03,150
Zhu Yingtai fell in love with a young man

355
00:32:04,150 --> 00:32:07,150
but she was forced to marry another man.

356
00:32:08,150 --> 00:32:12,150
When the young man found out, he was heartbroken and died later.

357
00:32:13,150 --> 00:32:15,150
The day that Zhu Yingtai had to get married,

358
00:32:16,150 --> 00:32:18,150
she paid her respects at the grave of the man she loved.

359
00:32:19,150 --> 00:32:23,150
Then after that, she threw herself into the grave to commit suicide.

360
00:32:25,150 --> 00:32:26,150
Tian.

361
00:32:28,150 --> 00:32:31,150
Why did you tell me this story?

362
00:32:32,150 --> 00:32:34,150
I just want to know

363
00:32:35,150 --> 00:32:37,150
if you have your own young man?

364
00:32:38,150 --> 00:32:39,150
Tian.

365
00:32:44,150 --> 00:32:48,150
Pin, don't you feel sorry for that young man?

366
00:32:54,150 --> 00:32:56,150
Yes, I do.

367
00:32:57,150 --> 00:32:59,150
But I also have to think about my father's feelings.

368
00:33:01,150 --> 00:33:02,150
I know that

369
00:33:03,150 --> 00:33:05,150
but you have to think about your own feelings as well.

370
00:33:08,150 --> 00:33:12,150
Would you exchange your whole life's happiness with someone you don't love?

371
00:33:18,150 --> 00:33:20,150
Think about it carefully.

372
00:33:21,150 --> 00:33:22,150
Is marrying me

373
00:33:23,150 --> 00:33:27,150
the only way to get the palace back from my mother?

374
00:33:29,150 --> 00:33:30,150
Tian.

375
00:33:32,150 --> 00:33:35,150
I don't have dignity at all, do I?

376
00:33:36,150 --> 00:33:37,150
That I have to marry for money.

377
00:33:38,150 --> 00:33:39,150
It's not like that.

378
00:33:40,150 --> 00:33:42,150
I understand that you have a duty.

379
00:33:43,150 --> 00:33:47,150
For me, you are grateful to your family.

380
00:33:48,150 --> 00:33:51,150
But I want you to think well.

381
00:33:51,750 --> 00:33:53,150
Choose well between love and duty.

382
00:33:54,150 --> 00:33:56,150
True love is rare.

383
00:33:58,150 --> 00:34:00,150
But I believe that you've found one.

384
00:34:01,150 --> 00:34:03,150
I don't want you to lose your love.

385
00:34:04,150 --> 00:34:09,150
Like Zhu Yingtai jumping into the grave to follow the man she loved.

386
00:34:10,150 --> 00:34:13,150
Tian, thank you very much.

387
00:34:15,150 --> 00:34:17,150
You are right.

388
00:34:18,150 --> 00:34:20,150
I should not solve problems with marriage.

389
00:34:21,150 --> 00:34:23,150
There must be another way.

390
00:34:24,150 --> 00:34:28,150
I should earn money to redeem the palace mortgaged to Aunt Li.

391
00:34:31,150 --> 00:34:35,150
I can be your good brother and friend to you.

392
00:34:37,150 --> 00:34:39,150
But I can't be your good lover.

393
00:34:40,150 --> 00:34:44,150
Try to figure out who that person is.

394
00:34:45,150 --> 00:34:47,150
I believe that you have met him.

395
00:34:50,150 --> 00:34:51,150
Fight for the one you love.

396
00:34:53,150 --> 00:34:56,150
Yes, he's a good man.

397
00:34:57,150 --> 00:34:58,150
When I am next to him,

398
00:35:00,150 --> 00:35:03,150
I'm happy and forget all the problems.

399
00:35:14,150 --> 00:35:16,150
Yang must be happy.

400
00:35:17,150 --> 00:35:18,150
Tian.

401
00:35:19,150 --> 00:35:22,150
I haven't said a word that it was Yang.

402
00:35:30,150 --> 00:35:31,150
Yang.

403
00:35:43,150 --> 00:35:45,150
Pin, Pin.

404
00:35:46,150 --> 00:35:47,150
Wait for me.

405
00:35:50,150 --> 00:35:51,150
Pin.

406
00:36:00,150 --> 00:36:03,150
You are so rude, eavesdropping on other people.

407
00:36:07,150 --> 00:36:08,150
You are smiling?

408
00:36:08,650 --> 00:36:10,150
I smile because I'm happy

409
00:36:10,650 --> 00:36:13,150
that you have decided not to marry Tian.

410
00:36:14,150 --> 00:36:15,150
Why are you glad?

411
00:36:16,150 --> 00:36:18,150
You want this to happen, right?

412
00:36:19,150 --> 00:36:21,150
Because you've always been interfering.

413
00:36:22,150 --> 00:36:23,150
I'm really glad

414
00:36:24,150 --> 00:36:26,150
that you will fight for the man you love.

415
00:36:28,150 --> 00:36:32,150
I will fight for the one I love, not you.

416
00:36:32,550 --> 00:36:33,150
A false claim.

417
00:36:36,150 --> 00:36:38,150
So disappointed.

418
00:36:39,150 --> 00:36:41,150
You're walking away already.

419
00:36:42,150 --> 00:36:44,150
Let's fight together.

420
00:36:52,150 --> 00:36:53,150
Don't worry.

421
00:36:54,150 --> 00:36:57,150
I definitely won't let you face your problems alone.

422
00:37:00,150 --> 00:37:01,150
Anyway,

423
00:37:02,150 --> 00:37:05,150
If you have to redeem the palace from Madam Li, how much money do you need?

424
00:37:07,150 --> 00:37:08,150
Hundreds of thousands.

425
00:37:10,150 --> 00:37:12,150
Before I refuse my father's request for marriage,

426
00:37:13,150 --> 00:37:15,150
I need to find a way to get back the palace.

427
00:37:16,150 --> 00:37:19,150
Otherwise, he wouldn't agree for sure.

428
00:37:21,150 --> 00:37:23,150
We'll work together to find a way out.

429
00:37:24,150 --> 00:37:28,150
This young man won't definitely die alone with a broken heart.

430
00:37:35,150 --> 00:37:36,150
Oh.

431
00:38:09,150 --> 00:38:10,150
Bua.

432
00:38:11,150 --> 00:38:14,150
Yes, I'm here, Mr. Tian.

433
00:38:19,150 --> 00:38:21,150
What are these that you're carrying?

434
00:38:22,150 --> 00:38:25,150
I want you to teach me how to make shadow puppets

435
00:38:26,150 --> 00:38:27,150
that you used to tell me when I was a kid.

436
00:38:29,150 --> 00:38:33,150
Do you want to see it again?

437
00:38:33,650 --> 00:38:34,150
No.

438
00:38:35,150 --> 00:38:40,150
I promised my friend that I would take them to the movies.

439
00:38:41,150 --> 00:38:43,150
But this is a war time, so I can't do that.

440
00:38:43,850 --> 00:38:48,150
So I'm going to do the shadow puppet instead.

441
00:38:50,150 --> 00:38:52,150
How old are your friends?

442
00:38:52,850 --> 00:38:56,150
One is seven years old, another is nine.

443
00:38:57,150 --> 00:38:58,150
The other…

444
00:39:01,150 --> 00:39:03,150
is twenty years old.

445
00:39:04,150 --> 00:39:05,150
This one is unfriendly.

446
00:39:06,150 --> 00:39:09,150
His face is always sad. I don't know why he is suffering.

447
00:39:11,150 --> 00:39:14,150
I haven't seen you smile like this in a long time.

448
00:39:15,150 --> 00:39:18,150
I want to get to know your friends too.

449
00:39:20,150 --> 00:39:22,150
Draw it like that.

450
00:39:23,150 --> 00:39:26,150
Keep it close together. So when you cut it, you'll be able to see it clearly.

451
00:39:27,150 --> 00:39:28,150
Yes.

452
00:41:16,150 --> 00:41:17,150
Sir.

453
00:41:17,650 --> 00:41:19,150
Drink some herbal medicine.

454
00:41:20,150 --> 00:41:22,150
You'll feel relaxed.

455
00:41:31,150 --> 00:41:33,150
Anything that you can take a break from,

456
00:41:33,850 --> 00:41:35,150
please stop for a while.

457
00:41:36,150 --> 00:41:37,150
Or you'll be sick.

458
00:41:39,150 --> 00:41:42,150
The doctor often warned that you should rest a lot.

459
00:41:49,150 --> 00:41:50,150
Thank you.

460
00:41:54,150 --> 00:41:56,150
I want to take a break as well.

461
00:41:58,150 --> 00:42:00,150
Letting Tian take care of all businesses

462
00:42:01,150 --> 00:42:02,150
if he's ready.

463
00:42:05,150 --> 00:42:07,150
But now our home is in so many chaos.

464
00:42:09,150 --> 00:42:11,150
Dong's body was replaced.

465
00:42:13,150 --> 00:42:15,150
I don't know if Li was involved in it.

466
00:42:17,150 --> 00:42:19,150
And Chan too.

467
00:42:20,150 --> 00:42:23,150
I don't know if she told Ma about our family matter.

468
00:42:25,150 --> 00:42:27,150
I really don't understand

469
00:42:29,150 --> 00:42:31,150
why they did that.

470
00:42:34,150 --> 00:42:37,150
There must be only one reason

471
00:42:38,150 --> 00:42:39,150
as a driving force that can make a mother

472
00:42:40,150 --> 00:42:43,150
do anything big like that.

473
00:42:44,150 --> 00:42:45,150
It is for children.

474
00:42:54,150 --> 00:42:56,150
About Dong's body that had been switched,

475
00:42:58,150 --> 00:42:59,150
If Li is behind this,

476
00:43:00,150 --> 00:43:04,150
that means that she is involved in Dong's death.

477
00:43:07,150 --> 00:43:10,150
I will let the authorities fully punish her.

478
00:43:11,150 --> 00:43:12,150
As for Chan,

479
00:43:13,150 --> 00:43:15,150
if she was the one who told Ma about this,

480
00:43:16,150 --> 00:43:18,150
I wouldn't let her get away as well.

481
00:43:20,150 --> 00:43:23,150
She knows that Ma is ready to stab me from the back any time

482
00:43:24,150 --> 00:43:25,150
and she still decides to do that.

483
00:43:55,150 --> 00:43:57,150
Apart from Zhang,

484
00:43:58,150 --> 00:43:59,150
I never trusted anyone again.

485
00:44:02,150 --> 00:44:05,150
I ended up like today probably because of karma

486
00:44:06,150 --> 00:44:08,150
that I put pressure on Zhang.

487
00:44:09,150 --> 00:44:12,150
I said he was a homosexual that he had to kill himself.

488
00:44:27,150 --> 00:44:28,150
Zhang.

489
00:44:32,150 --> 00:44:34,150
Zhang, Zhang.

490
00:44:34,450 --> 00:44:35,150
Zhang.

491
00:44:35,850 --> 00:44:44,150
One day, I wish you feel the pain that I had.

492
00:44:44,750 --> 00:44:45,150
Zhang.

493
00:44:48,150 --> 00:44:50,150
Zhang, Zhang.

494
00:44:55,150 --> 00:44:57,150
Ten years have passed.

495
00:44:59,150 --> 00:45:00,150
I still feel guilty

496
00:45:02,150 --> 00:45:04,150
that I judged him like that.

497
00:45:06,150 --> 00:45:08,150
No matter how many years have passed,

498
00:45:09,150 --> 00:45:11,150
that feeling of guilt never faded.

499
00:45:12,150 --> 00:45:14,150
I understand you.

500
00:45:15,150 --> 00:45:17,150
But you did your best.

501
00:45:18,150 --> 00:45:19,150
But not good enough.

502
00:45:21,150 --> 00:45:23,150
Otherwise he wouldn't have died.

503
00:45:26,150 --> 00:45:28,150
If there's anything I can atone for my mistake,

504
00:45:29,150 --> 00:45:31,150
I am ready to do it.

505
00:45:34,150 --> 00:45:35,150
The rest of my life,

506
00:45:37,150 --> 00:45:40,150
I just want only peace in our family.

507
00:46:01,150 --> 00:46:03,150
Mei, Fu.

508
00:46:03,550 --> 00:46:04,150
Tian.

509
00:46:07,150 --> 00:46:10,150
I told you not to come here again.

510
00:46:11,150 --> 00:46:12,150
Why can't I?

511
00:46:13,150 --> 00:46:16,150
I didn't come to see you. I came here for Mei and Fu.

512
00:46:18,150 --> 00:46:19,150
But they are my siblings.

513
00:46:20,150 --> 00:46:22,150
I don't allow it. Go back now.

514
00:46:22,350 --> 00:46:25,150
I won't. I made a promise with them already.

515
00:46:26,150 --> 00:46:29,150
Jiu, don't chase Tian away.

516
00:46:30,150 --> 00:46:33,150
Please, he brought us a movie. I want to see a movie.

517
00:46:34,150 --> 00:46:37,150
Please, Jiu. Please.

518
00:46:38,150 --> 00:46:41,150
Why are you such a mean brother?

519
00:47:00,150 --> 00:47:02,150
Once upon a time,

520
00:47:03,150 --> 00:47:05,150
In a Mount Emei,

521
00:47:08,150 --> 00:47:10,150
There is Bai Suzhen.

522
00:47:11,150 --> 00:47:15,150
She is Madam White Snake who has practiced disciplined training for thousand years.

523
00:47:20,150 --> 00:47:25,150
She transformed herself into a human.

524
00:47:31,150 --> 00:47:33,150
Ta-da / Whoa.

525
00:47:36,150 --> 00:47:39,150
When Madam White Snake came to live in the human world,

526
00:47:40,150 --> 00:47:42,150
she fell in love with a young man.

527
00:47:53,150 --> 00:47:55,150
Tian, what about the young man?

528
00:47:56,150 --> 00:47:58,150
Wait a minute.

529
00:47:59,150 --> 00:48:00,150
I can't hold it in both hands.

530
00:48:00,350 --> 00:48:03,150
Jiu, help Tian hold it.

531
00:48:04,150 --> 00:48:05,150
Quickly.

532
00:48:05,250 --> 00:48:06,150
Hurry, Jiu.

533
00:48:24,150 --> 00:48:30,150
Although the love between Bai Suzhen and her lover had many obstacles,

534
00:48:31,150 --> 00:48:34,150
they can get through them until the end.

535
00:48:42,150 --> 00:48:49,150
And finally, Bai Suzhen married the man she loved

536
00:48:49,550 --> 00:48:51,150
and lived with him happily.

537
00:49:42,150 --> 00:49:44,150
Don't come here again in the future.

538
00:49:45,150 --> 00:49:46,150
I beg you.

539
00:49:47,150 --> 00:49:49,150
Why?

540
00:49:50,150 --> 00:49:53,150
I already told you that this is not your place.

541
00:49:57,150 --> 00:49:58,150
Madam White Snake

542
00:49:59,150 --> 00:50:01,150
was imprisoned in a pagoda eventually

543
00:50:02,150 --> 00:50:04,150
because she didn't know her place, right?

544
00:50:06,150 --> 00:50:08,150
But that's just a legend.

545
00:50:09,150 --> 00:50:11,150
Somehow it was just a story.

546
00:50:12,150 --> 00:50:14,150
Perhaps Madam White Snake

547
00:50:15,150 --> 00:50:19,150
lived in the human world with the man she loved.

548
00:50:22,150 --> 00:50:23,150
You really don't listen to anyone.

549
00:50:25,150 --> 00:50:27,150
I'll listen to you if you have enough reasons.

550
00:50:29,150 --> 00:50:33,150
If you see me here again next time, you can scold me then.

551
00:50:34,150 --> 00:50:35,150
Thank you for sending me.

552
00:51:00,150 --> 00:51:01,150
The torch.

553
00:51:09,150 --> 00:51:10,150
Sir.

554
00:51:12,150 --> 00:51:15,150
Good you're here, I'm going to find you at home.

555
00:51:22,150 --> 00:51:24,150
This is your sister's medicine.

556
00:51:25,150 --> 00:51:26,150
Thank you, sir.

557
00:51:28,150 --> 00:51:31,150
Since Mei got your medicine, she's getting better.

558
00:51:32,150 --> 00:51:35,150
Then remember this well that your sister

559
00:51:36,150 --> 00:51:37,150
depend on Mr. Ma's medicine.

560
00:51:38,150 --> 00:51:39,150
Otherwise, she would have died long ago.

561
00:51:40,150 --> 00:51:42,150
You should be very grateful.

562
00:51:44,150 --> 00:51:46,150
Don't say that.

563
00:51:48,150 --> 00:51:49,150
Jiu

564
00:51:50,150 --> 00:51:52,150
is already a grateful man.

565
00:51:53,150 --> 00:51:54,150
Right?

566
00:52:01,150 --> 00:52:04,150
Would you mind sharing the formula of the medicine you gave to my sister?

567
00:52:05,150 --> 00:52:07,150
So I can know exactly what medicine it is.

568
00:52:08,150 --> 00:52:10,150
She's not getting better taking other medicine.

569
00:52:11,150 --> 00:52:14,150
But her condition is back to normal completely when she takes yours.

570
00:52:15,150 --> 00:52:18,150
The next time when Mei suffers a relapse, I don't need to bother you again.

571
00:52:19,150 --> 00:52:21,150
I can't give it to you.

572
00:52:22,150 --> 00:52:24,150
You have to bother me again and again.

573
00:52:26,150 --> 00:52:27,150
Get ready.

574
00:52:28,150 --> 00:52:32,150
I will have a job for you soon.

575
00:52:54,150 --> 00:52:55,150
Hey.

576
00:52:56,150 --> 00:52:57,150
What's the matter again?

577
00:52:58,150 --> 00:53:01,150
Just now I saw you talking to…

578
00:53:01,350 --> 00:53:02,150
Are you spying on me?

579
00:53:03,150 --> 00:53:04,150
Not like that.

580
00:53:05,150 --> 00:53:09,150
I forgot my torch so I come back and saw it.

581
00:53:12,150 --> 00:53:14,150
Did you know that that man was a bad guy?

582
00:53:15,150 --> 00:53:16,150
Don't mess with him, okay?

583
00:53:17,150 --> 00:53:18,150
Thanks for warning me.

584
00:53:20,150 --> 00:53:23,150
But he is rich and powerful.

585
00:53:25,150 --> 00:53:26,150
I have to depend on him.

586
00:53:27,150 --> 00:53:29,150
So don't rely on him next time.

587
00:53:30,150 --> 00:53:32,150
People like me don't have much choice.

588
00:53:34,150 --> 00:53:36,150
Sometimes I had to do it.

589
00:53:37,150 --> 00:53:39,150
The things that good people don't do.

590
00:53:40,150 --> 00:53:42,150
Then next time,

591
00:53:43,150 --> 00:53:46,150
let me be your choice too.

592
00:53:47,150 --> 00:53:50,150
If you are in trouble, come to me.

593
00:53:51,150 --> 00:53:52,150
My father can help you.

594
00:53:55,150 --> 00:53:56,150
Who is your father?

595
00:53:58,150 --> 00:53:59,150
You shouldn't know about it.

596
00:54:00,150 --> 00:54:03,150
You'll say that I'm rich and you're poor again.

597
00:54:03,550 --> 00:54:05,150
The two of us are different.

598
00:54:07,150 --> 00:54:08,150
Just remember that

599
00:54:09,150 --> 00:54:10,150
I can help you.

600
00:54:11,150 --> 00:54:14,150
The two of us can be friends and that's enough.

601
00:54:49,150 --> 00:54:51,150
You're so good.

602
00:54:51,550 --> 00:54:55,150
Look at my work. My stitches can't compare to you.

603
00:54:56,150 --> 00:55:00,150
Madam, you just start practicing embroidery.

604
00:55:01,150 --> 00:55:04,150
Yours is pretty already. If you do it more often, you will be better at it.

605
00:55:05,150 --> 00:55:09,150
Tian must be very happy that you embroider the shirt for him.

606
00:55:10,150 --> 00:55:14,150
I intend to give him on the day of taking the position of the association leader.

607
00:55:16,150 --> 00:55:20,150
Are you embroidering a shirt for Tian to wear on the day of the taking the position?

608
00:55:21,150 --> 00:55:23,150
I'm afraid he won't have a chance to use it.

609
00:55:24,150 --> 00:55:26,150
What do you mean?

610
00:55:27,150 --> 00:55:31,150
Do you think that Yang will take the position of association leader instead of Tian?

611
00:55:33,150 --> 00:55:35,150
I didn't say that.

612
00:55:35,650 --> 00:55:39,150
Tian is perfect without flaws.

613
00:55:40,150 --> 00:55:43,150
It must have been him only to inherit the position.

614
00:55:43,650 --> 00:55:44,150
Right?

615
00:55:45,150 --> 00:55:48,150
Yes? So is there still Mr. Tian's secret or not?

616
00:55:48,350 --> 00:55:50,150
Hey, I'm sarcastic.

617
00:55:52,150 --> 00:55:53,150
Madam Chan.

618
00:55:54,150 --> 00:55:56,150
You're living in the same house. Please don't argue.

619
00:55:57,150 --> 00:55:59,150
Don't teach me.

620
00:55:59,450 --> 00:56:01,150
Do you think you're a good person?

621
00:56:01,650 --> 00:56:05,150
You act like you're neutral, despite the fact that you are on Madam's side.

622
00:56:05,650 --> 00:56:06,150
Chan.

623
00:56:07,150 --> 00:56:10,150
If you are not happy to see other people happy,

624
00:56:11,150 --> 00:56:13,150
just close your eyes and walks past us.

625
00:56:14,150 --> 00:56:15,150
Why would you want a fight here?

626
00:56:16,150 --> 00:56:20,150
I'm not good at closing my eyes. It's someone else's favorite job.

627
00:56:23,150 --> 00:56:27,150
Just wait and see, if the police can find out that the body is not Dong,

628
00:56:28,150 --> 00:56:30,150
there must be a search for Dong's body.

629
00:56:31,150 --> 00:56:33,150
This time, you'll know the truth.

630
00:56:56,150 --> 00:56:59,150
Why does Mr. Ma let us watch over these corpses?

631
00:57:00,150 --> 00:57:02,150
He said they were important corpses.

632
00:57:03,150 --> 00:57:04,150
Just do it. Don't complain.

633
00:57:15,150 --> 00:57:19,150
Mr. Ma is very cautious, sending two subordinates to watch it.

634
00:57:20,150 --> 00:57:24,150
That warehouse is also near the temple hall and the undertaker's house.

635
00:57:25,150 --> 00:57:27,150
Both monks and villagers are there.

636
00:57:28,150 --> 00:57:29,150
I can't find a right time yet.

637
00:57:34,150 --> 00:57:35,150
That's bad.

638
00:57:36,150 --> 00:57:38,150
If we let it go on, we'll be in trouble.

639
00:57:41,150 --> 00:57:42,150
What should we do?

640
00:57:43,150 --> 00:57:45,150
I will find a way to handle that body.

641
00:58:23,150 --> 00:58:25,150
I must prepare to be ready.

642
00:58:26,150 --> 00:58:27,150
I have to make beetle orchid.

643
00:58:28,150 --> 00:58:29,150
Jia.

644
00:58:30,150 --> 00:58:31,150
I've been wondering for a long time.

645
00:58:32,150 --> 00:58:34,150
How did these plant originate?

646
00:58:35,150 --> 00:58:38,150
The beetle orchids originate from the blood sucking mushrooms.

647
00:58:40,150 --> 00:58:44,150
Usually they grows on insects, not human.

648
00:58:45,150 --> 00:58:48,150
But there are ways to make it grow in people.

649
00:58:49,150 --> 00:58:50,150
How do you do it?

650
00:58:52,150 --> 00:58:55,150
I mixes a few secret herbs.

651
00:58:57,150 --> 00:58:58,150
But the important is…

652
00:59:03,150 --> 00:59:04,150
human blood.

653
00:59:25,150 --> 00:59:27,150
Do you have to do this?

654
00:59:29,150 --> 00:59:31,150
It will remember to suck the blood of people.

655
00:59:33,150 --> 00:59:36,150
If someone inhales or consume it,

656
00:59:37,150 --> 00:59:39,150
the poison will make that person's body numb

657
00:59:40,150 --> 00:59:41,150
and unable to move.

658
00:59:46,150 --> 00:59:50,150
It will enter and suck the person's flesh as food.

659
00:59:52,150 --> 00:59:55,150
the poisonous mushrooms will grow all over the body.

660
01:00:01,150 --> 01:00:05,150
That person will suffocate because he or she becomes food for the poisonous mushrooms.

661
01:00:07,150 --> 01:00:11,150
So the mushrooms that grow from people aren't dangerous, are they?

662
01:00:11,550 --> 01:00:12,150
Yes, Madam.

663
01:00:13,150 --> 01:00:16,150
The mushrooms that grow out of humans cannot reproduce.

664
01:00:17,150 --> 01:00:18,150
In addition to beetle orchid,

665
01:00:20,150 --> 01:00:23,150
I still have a lot of orchid for different purposes.

666
01:00:24,150 --> 01:00:28,150
If the blood-sucking mushroom grow on other insects,

667
01:00:28,650 --> 01:00:32,150
it will turn out to have different properties.

668
01:00:34,150 --> 01:00:39,150
These orchids can help us protect Mr. Tian's secret.

669
01:01:09,150 --> 01:01:10,150
Li.

670
01:01:11,150 --> 01:01:12,150
Li.

671
01:01:13,150 --> 01:01:14,150
Where are you?

672
01:01:16,150 --> 01:01:17,150
Li.

673
01:01:18,150 --> 01:01:19,150
Li.

674
01:01:20,150 --> 01:01:21,150
Li.

675
01:01:22,150 --> 01:01:23,150
Where are you?

676
01:01:25,150 --> 01:01:27,150
Tian. / Father.

677
01:01:27,250 --> 01:01:28,150
Where is your mom?

678
01:01:29,150 --> 01:01:31,150
I didn't see her. Please go to the bunker first.

679
01:01:34,150 --> 01:01:35,150
Sir.

680
01:01:35,350 --> 01:01:36,150
Chan.

681
01:01:37,150 --> 01:01:40,150
Yang, did you see Mother and Aunt Jia?

682
01:01:40,650 --> 01:01:42,150
No. How about this?

683
01:01:42,450 --> 01:01:44,150
You and Nuan take Father to the bunker first.

684
01:01:44,450 --> 01:01:46,150
Tian and I will go find Madam Li. Go.

685
01:01:46,550 --> 01:01:47,150
Yes.

686
01:01:47,450 --> 01:01:48,150
Please take care of him.

687
01:01:48,350 --> 01:01:49,150
Nuan, take care of Father and Mother.

688
01:01:50,250 --> 01:01:51,150
Yes.

689
01:01:57,150 --> 01:02:00,150
Jia, you have to be very careful, it's dangerous.

690
01:02:01,150 --> 01:02:02,150
Or should I go with you.

691
01:02:02,450 --> 01:02:03,150
No, Madam.

692
01:02:04,150 --> 01:02:06,150
Others will wonder where you have been.

693
01:02:06,550 --> 01:02:07,150
Don't worry.

694
01:02:08,150 --> 01:02:09,150
I have beetle orchid with me.

695
01:02:10,150 --> 01:02:12,150
I can definitely handle Mr. Ma's subordinates.

696
01:02:16,150 --> 01:02:18,150
Madam Li, Madam! / Mother!

697
01:02:22,150 --> 01:02:23,150
Mother!

698
01:02:24,150 --> 01:02:26,150
Or is Madam with Aunt Jia?

699
01:02:28,150 --> 01:02:29,150
Mother!

700
01:02:29,550 --> 01:02:30,150
Aunt Jia!

701
01:02:32,150 --> 01:02:33,150
Aunt Jia! / Mother!

702
01:02:33,350 --> 01:02:34,150
Mother!

703
01:02:34,350 --> 01:02:35,150
Tian.

704
01:02:35,350 --> 01:02:36,150
Madam, Aunt Jia.

705
01:02:37,150 --> 01:02:38,150
Hurry up to the bunker.

706
01:02:38,350 --> 01:02:39,150
Let's go.

707
01:02:39,350 --> 01:02:40,150
I still can't go, Sir.

708
01:02:41,150 --> 01:02:44,150
Why? Let's go together to the bunker now.

709
01:02:45,150 --> 01:02:48,150
I am boiling herb. Let me put out the fire and collect the important things first.

710
01:02:48,450 --> 01:02:49,150
Aunt Jia.

711
01:02:49,350 --> 01:02:50,150
Aunt Jia.

712
01:02:50,350 --> 01:02:52,150
Tian, hurry up and take me away. I'm scared.

713
01:02:52,450 --> 01:02:54,150
Let's go. Yang, go.

714
01:02:54,350 --> 01:02:55,150
I'll be right behind you.

715
01:02:55,750 --> 01:02:56,150
Aunt Jia.

716
01:02:56,350 --> 01:02:57,150
Madam, hurry up, let's go.

717
01:02:59,150 --> 01:03:00,150
Hurry up.

718
01:03:25,150 --> 01:03:26,150
Hey!

719
01:03:27,150 --> 01:03:28,150
Hey!

720
01:03:58,150 --> 01:03:59,150
Hey, what are you doing?

721
01:05:06,150 --> 01:05:07,150
It's here.

722
01:06:26,150 --> 01:06:27,150
Is everyone safe?

723
01:06:28,150 --> 01:06:31,150
Yes, Sir. All the workers fled to the bunker in time.

724
01:06:32,150 --> 01:06:34,150
Fortunately, the bomb didn't land in our house this time.

725
01:06:37,150 --> 01:06:39,150
Where is Jia?

726
01:06:39,350 --> 01:06:40,150
Where did she go?

727
01:06:41,150 --> 01:06:45,150
That's right. She said she would quickly follow us.

728
01:06:47,150 --> 01:06:51,150
Everyone, when they escaped into the bunker, has anyone met Auntie Jia?

729
01:07:01,150 --> 01:07:05,150
Or is she killed by a bomb, Madam?

730
01:07:05,250 --> 01:07:07,150
Nuan, don't be silly.

731
01:07:11,150 --> 01:07:13,150
Aunt Jia, she's there.

732
01:07:20,150 --> 01:07:23,150
Jia, where did you hide?

733
01:07:23,450 --> 01:07:25,150
I've heard that you didn't go to hide with the workers.

734
01:07:26,150 --> 01:07:27,150
Everyone is worried about you.

735
01:07:35,150 --> 01:07:37,150
It's when the siren rang, I had no time.

736
01:07:38,150 --> 01:07:41,150
So after collecting everything, I went to hide in the forest near my house.

737
01:07:42,150 --> 01:07:43,150
It's dark there.

738
01:07:53,150 --> 01:07:54,150
Aunt Jia

739
01:07:56,150 --> 01:07:57,150
What happened to your hand?

740
01:08:02,150 --> 01:08:06,150
When I went to put out the fire from boiling herbs, I was in a hurry.

741
01:08:06,350 --> 01:08:08,150
So my hand hit the herbal pot.

742
01:08:12,150 --> 01:08:14,150
But everything is fine now.

743
01:08:33,150 --> 01:08:34,150
Yang, Yang.

744
01:08:36,150 --> 01:08:38,150
When you called Jia to come to the bunker,

745
01:08:38,350 --> 01:08:39,150
what was she doing?

746
01:08:40,150 --> 01:08:41,150
I didn't see what she was doing.

747
01:08:42,150 --> 01:08:43,150
But Aunt Jia said

748
01:08:44,150 --> 01:08:47,150
she would pout the fire and collect the important things first.

749
01:08:48,150 --> 01:08:49,150
That's strange.

750
01:08:50,150 --> 01:08:51,150
Usually, she never leaves Madam Li.

751
01:08:52,150 --> 01:08:56,150
Since it was dangerous and explosion like this, why did she leave her boss?

752
01:08:57,150 --> 01:08:58,150
Mom, don't mess with her.

753
01:09:00,150 --> 01:09:01,150
What is more important than life?

754
01:09:02,150 --> 01:09:04,150
Taking the risk to collect things when there was an explosion?

755
01:09:07,150 --> 01:09:09,150
I think there must be something.

756
01:09:53,150 --> 01:09:54,150
The warehouse at the temple was completely burned down?

757
01:09:55,150 --> 01:09:56,150
How dare you?

758
01:09:56,350 --> 01:09:57,750
No one will respect you in the future.

759
01:09:58,150 --> 01:09:59,150
Tian! / Stop!

760
01:10:00,150 --> 01:10:01,150
I have a doubt.

761
01:10:01,350 --> 01:10:03,150
Has anyone else known this?

762
01:10:03,350 --> 01:10:05,150
This mushroom is probably related to the chaos in our house.

763
01:10:05,350 --> 01:10:06,150
What's this?

764
01:10:07,150 --> 01:10:10,150
I will let you kill the Song's eldest son.

765
01:10:11,150 --> 01:10:14,150
One more month and a half, Tian has to marry Pin.

766
01:10:14,350 --> 01:10:16,150
I won't be able to find the money to redeem the palace in time.

767
01:10:16,650 --> 01:10:19,150
You let someone call me to come here, what's the matter?

768
01:10:19,350 --> 01:10:21,150
I'd like you to meet someone.

769
01:10:22,150 --> 01:10:25,150
I know that your secret makes you unable to marry Pin.

770
01:10:25,350 --> 01:10:27,150
But other people don't know this.
